{"tid":363792,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔知道自己想點","createTime":"2017-08-18T01:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T05:00:31.000Z","uid":6181,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"759e23a668adc6bf17409ad23c58948753613cb8","tid":363792,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"日日返工好似冇左靈魂咁<br />\n<br />\n好似每日每個星期每個月發生既事都係重覆咁, 返工放工訓覺月尾出糧月頭昐月尾<br />\n<br />\n每日都望日子快D過, 快D到月尾出糧<br />\n<br />\n但日日又唔想返工, 真係同條咸魚冇分別<br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇人係鍾意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再加上G鋒坐監, 更加對香港冇昐望<br />\n<br />\n睇唔見香港既將來, 更加睇唔見自己既將來<br />\n<br />\n過得一日得一日<br />\n<br />\n開工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db363d46c2809949e1de96c0d6f26df6d88c6662","tid":363792,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"做人真係好攰"},{"pid":"bcde9810d4cdf2548a287a3f32c42682602caf95","tid":363792,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"再加上G鋒坐監, 更加對香港冇昐望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339a05c3d665b4495cb1c3a8b51d65defe40a9b2","tid":363792,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:24:19.000Z","msg":"Ptgf: 拓海，你要搵一個屬於你自己既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b0f25ec1ffc7867f482f5aadef70d2b426e73c","tid":363792,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ptgf: 拓海，你要搵一個屬於你自己既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哦知道"},{"pid":"cfbe38d4361929f39bd3711986779fb77a7cb125","tid":363792,"uid":22460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"痾埋屎準備翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2063d2b1d45936aa88cb89748207dd63b980c